divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking a picture of a very strange looking sunset. After taking thepicture I never checked it until later when I observed what appears to be a disclike object moving from left to right. I think I saw movement when I took thepicture but I cant saw with 100 per cent certainty. None of the other 6 peoplepresent saw or heard anything.
Summary: Taking picture of cloud formations and sunset.
